data.description: Highly Motivated Sellers!  Nearly 3 acres, and 5 bedrooms in this 2019 manufactured home in Guston!! Enjoy plenty of outdoor yard space, and a covered back deck with views of the woods. This convenient location is on a quiet cul-de-sac, it's less than 7 miles from Irvington to the west, and only about a 20 minute drive to Ft. Knox to the east. The large living room, fireplace, and open floor plan make this home a great place to relax and entertain. Schedule your showing today!
